 PIVOT operator :-
 -----------------------

  => operator used to convert rows into columns 
  => operator used to display data in matrix form
  => operator used for cross tabulation 

 SELECT *
 FROM (SELECT required data)  <alias>
 PIVOT
 (
     aggr-expr  FOR  colname IN (v1,v2,v3,---)
